      class  TouchPointDao
      TouchPointDao (Dao == Database access object) provides a range of standard function calls required for object instance life-cycle management in addition to functionality geared towards the updates system tables which are used primarily by processes to poll any updates to objects they are not directly managing but still need to monitor.
